text:

Washington D.C., Oct. 14(ANI): Emilia Clarke has been crowned as the "Sexiest Women Alive" by Esquire magazine. After receiving the honour, the 28-year-old actress stripped down for a rauncy photo shoot with the magazine, in which she is seen showing off hr incredible body as she poses in lingerie, reports E! Online. The 'Game of Thrones' star also went topless in some pictures, while in others she even appears to be nude with just a sheet covering her. (ANI) Â»
